description: Redevelopment of site involving the demolition of 1314 existing residential units and construction of 2977 new residential units providing a total of 3440 units on the estate, provision of approximately 9074sqm replacement retail (Class A1), office (Class A2) food and drink (Class A3) and social and community (Class D1) uses and associated public and private open space, car parking and access arrangements.
